      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «اَلْمُنْجِيَاتُ إِطْعَامُ اَلطَّعَامِ وَ إِفْشَاءُ اَلسَّلاَمِ وَ اَلصَّلاَةُ بِاللَّيْلِ وَ اَلنَّاسُ نِيَامٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1719 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"The acts that bring salvation are feeding the hungry, spreading peace, and praying at night while people are asleep.\""
        ]
      }
